{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1b9fad6374","title":"谢富治在北京工代会传达周总理江青对抓“五·一六”的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"62390abf11","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":4,"articleId":"1b9fad6374"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"/books/jqjianghua.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"},{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"}]},"publication_details":{"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"420f5f994b","type":"title","text":"谢富治在北京工代会传达周总理江青对抓“五·一六”的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"1b9fad6374"},{"id":"c1e7394497","type":"appellation","text":"谢富治说：","index":1,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"1b9fad6374"},{"id":"bdbf518c67","type":"paragraph","text":"“抓 5.16到处乱抓。在接见工代会第一天会议上，江青同志还讲了话，这个没有向大家传达，也应该告诉同志们。”“江青同志说：不要到处抓 5.16，哪里有那么多 5.16呢？总理也说：不要借题发挥。江青同志还在会上讲：不要什么都扣 5.16的帽子。”","index":2,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"1b9fad6374"}],"page":{"id":"0ed117b0ae","publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"1b9fad6374","start":503,"end":503}}}},"__N_SSG":true}